Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(544,317)}取名叫「名古屋」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(85,370)}羽 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(56,482)}雞飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷雫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好參加此次會議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼雞棚要怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我已經查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的答案都在網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近有個建材超市哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去那裏買材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家一起去吧 這周雙休一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,32)}祝養雞委員會成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(216,85)}第一回會議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(106,125)}取名叫「名古屋」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(403,165)}羽 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,202)}雞飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,258)}雞棚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.99,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動之後再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同學一起度過的雙休
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.62,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了的話 就是那個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:01.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是碰面啊 時間地點啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 反正是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候是不是應該答應下來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:22.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖然說了喜歡 那也只是氣氛推動罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:35.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我這份心意沒有讓春感到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為社團活動結束的早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去裏面等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:57.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我不擅長和男生單獨相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要再來這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:12.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 那人好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 棒球少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐原同學你認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我經常來這裏玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說少年 你和春也是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是朋友不如說是同學啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打一局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:34.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輕易把錢借給別人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 球棒要這麼握著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉 我弟把鬧鐘弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 不是很帥氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去借啊 按揭貸款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 雞又不交稅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 別管他們了 我們去找材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:16.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色 金色 金色 茶色 黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 正好有些話要和你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同學 L尺寸是指什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿佐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮冬瓜你幹嗎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同學 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳 還以為會打起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 我連架都沒打過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們先到外面去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.63,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面 後面 水谷同學有危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 我們快跑吧 春！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑的真慢呢 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 對不起 夏目同學能幫忙買回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙可能還在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我過去幫忙提東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 你就陪著水谷同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:08:59.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:08.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過每次都被你嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用一隻手就把人扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己剛剛拒絕過的人說點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:33.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平常 一定會拒絕照顧雞這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日要你出來 你也絕對會拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:37.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人在奇怪的地方真是敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…是在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都買好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把木頭鋸成一段一段好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說要店員幫我們鋸好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種漂亮的雞屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們自己做根本不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:38.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說 我們選的還是最簡單易懂的網站了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說買那個小屋就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎麼了 怎麼了 已經累垮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋸子嗎？好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們要電鋸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電鋸的話早說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！我去拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:59.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去買一點冰 你們想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要GARIGARI蘇打冰棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要巨無霸巧克力冰淇淋夾心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能完成嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用這麼慌張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是真的有話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也覺得有點對不起春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但問題是從那之後就聯繫不上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那現在道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說對不對 水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之前傷害了人家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才想起道歉實在很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 想道歉的話就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:49.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要別打擾到我們做事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也學會察言觀色啊 我們是想讓你當和事佬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你們這群傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:10.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一下嘛 春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.43,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來找她說些話的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是不是呢？水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰准你碰雫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！臭小子 你聽人家說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你就討厭 山賢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.52,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能別動不動就動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.61,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙到底是幹什麼來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說想來和你和好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:39.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了表明心意他們好像要幫忙蓋雞屋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為什麼要幹這種蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:47.50,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的話 這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 早點說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊 一起來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好單純
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場景經常在電視上看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是好朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:06.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙真的好嗎 你喜歡這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買冰回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞了點路所以冰有點化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 變多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！超級可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.34,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個組合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.61,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好扶好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小水 這些人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使喚別人就可以不費力的完成 太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經過這些事 雞屋總算順利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幹了件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把名古屋帶來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 祝賀你哦 水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什麼都沒做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了不許碰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！混蛋！你夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有點煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周就可以把雞屋帶到學校去 好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:14.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得帶那種東西去會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們把雞小屋放到草叢裏就沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點可怕 不過春同學那些朋友真是不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我往這邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這邊 可以一起走一段路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期一見哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:42.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為什麼叫名古屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在吐槽太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞的名字的話名古屋不好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 送到這裏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你客氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和雫多待一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有勇氣抬頭看他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說人的一生的幸福和不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是上帝決定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過終點大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是「正負相消」的道理？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是一種詭辯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最近總是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說遇到雫是我的幸運的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之前都是些亂七八糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自從與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到的都是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡春！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼努力想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想像不出別人的心情是如何的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 就只能由我直接說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候春說了 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡我 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我讓你困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我已經喜歡上春了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…還真是坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你在那裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:45.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…並沒有讓我困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話…我還YY過各種下流的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事 你不用說出來也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情可能和雫不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道了我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想雫會不會離我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把剛剛說的那些話收回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等讓春喜歡上我之後 我再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:50.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為春說想和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.49,setting3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz332.913\pos(626,370)}阿三哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.49,setting3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz332.427\pos(365,435)}優山要來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫 別回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 隨便找個地方過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:30.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然如此輕鬆地推翻了我的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼…多麼麻煩的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉田 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雫 這位是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今晚不想回家住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆也 晚飯吃了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:09.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…陋室而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老媽不在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要住在客房吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 隨便找個地方過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間 忍不住想像了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雫做的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛不是看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有醃菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厲害啊 簡直就像鄉下的老婆婆似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不是說過別來這兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:12.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優山！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你家裏有座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在別人家裏 你這是什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 在家裏還學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不知道看向哪裏才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真閒啊 玩文字接龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:56.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是爸爸也總是只穿一條內褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是就這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微看一眼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡的話就到被窩裏睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我還帶了特產過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 滿善給我倒杯茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:40.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春真是個膽小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能躲我到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得樣子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 為什麼你們會在顏料噴霧販售處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:35.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:37.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為要塗鴉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往公共物品上塗鴉的行為是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:43.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己家的東西上塗鴉有什麼不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他家院子裏全是雕刻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:49.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說為什麼不良少年都愛往牆上塗鴉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那裏有面牆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:52.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:54.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是雕刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:02.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡藝術的有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人吃驚…
