Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:20.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:21.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧

